DOC_LEVEL: L1
MODULE: project-config
PATH: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md
DESCRIPTION: runtime dependencies, environment contract, and AI workflow rules

MANIFEST:
- package.json scripts: start, dev, test, test:unit, test:integration, typecheck, lint
- dependencies: dotenv, express, pino, screenshot-desktop, telegraf, zod
- devDependencies: typescript, eslint, @types/node

ENV_CONTRACT:
- telegram: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, ENABLE_TELEGRAM, ALLOWED_USER_IDS
- codebuddy bridge: CODEBUDDY_BIN, CODEBUDDY_PERMISSION_FLAG, CODEBUDDY_ECHO_STDIO, CODEBUDDY_HEARTBEAT_MS
- pipeline infra: PIPELINE_PROJECT_ROOT, PIPELINE_DIR, FEATURE_LIST_PATH, BUG_FIX_LIST_PATH, MAX_RETRIES, SESSION_TIMEOUT, HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL, AI_CLI, PRIZMKIT_PLATFORM
- web: WEB_HOST, WEB_PORT
- system exec: ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC, ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES, SYSTEM_EXEC_TIMEOUT_MS

PLATFORM_SETTINGS:
- .codebuddy/settings.json -> UserPromptSubmit reminder hook present
- CODEBUDDY.md -> PrizmKit protocol section already present

DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:
- outdated_major: dotenv, express, zod
- npm_audit_prod: 0

DECISIONS:
- 2026-03-09 | config-doc-init | lock platform=codebuddy and passive adoption defaults
- 2026-03-10 | f001-config-loader | unify pipeline infra env+argv loading via src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js and expose from src/config.js
- 2026-03-12 | f001-v2-tooling | tsconfig expanded to src/**/*.js, eslint rules baseline added (eqeqeq, no-undef, no-unused-vars, etc.)
